Busta 929:
Busta 929 have 16 songs on the Spotify Top 200 Weekly South Africa chart. 
 He first appeared on the chart on 14 January 2021. His most recent appearance has been on 12 October 2023. He has a total of 15.6 million streams. 
. His highest position on the chart is 1 for the song Ngixolele which was at this position on 04 November 2021
 The songs of his that have appeared on the chart are Beke Le Beke ... Ekseni ... Gqoz Gqoz ... Mamaye ... Mmapula ... Mswipeni ... Ngixolele ... Nompumelelo ... Paradise ... SDUDLA No Slenda ... Thixo Somandla ... Umsebenzi Wethu ... Umsebenzi Wethu - Interlude ... Umsebenzi Wethu 2.0 ... Usizo ... Uyavala
